# Background Processing Standards

Follow the canonical standard: **`.ai/standards/sidekiq-activejob.md`**

Key rules:
- Prefer ActiveJob as the interface; Sidekiq as the production adapter
- Keep `perform` thin — delegate to a Service Object
- Pass identifiers (IDs), never whole ActiveRecord objects
- Jobs must be idempotent and retry-safe
- Set explicit queues by latency class; protect the Sidekiq Web UI
- Never log secrets or PII in job arguments

